    Name of Module: PlannerUnit Purpose: Creates the data structure to hold planner information for a specific semester + year combination (e.g. Fall 2017) Inputs: String Semester, Int Year Used to ensure courses are stored in the proper unit; if no unit exists, a new one is created Outputs: PlannerUnit plannerUnit a planner unit for a LinkedUnit which is, in turn, for a Planner Submodules: None Author: Andrea Lee Date: 11/13/16 Reviewer: ???
